{
  "stem": "21817.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he worked with the local government and tried to get a passport that they should come over from Germany to Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because those two years before the war, the 1941 war started, it was normal relation between Germany and Poland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother received the passport with the kids to come to us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she was over there in, in Mlawa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But later on, she was transferred to a camp already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They organized a camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she wrote us, we have the passport, hopefully we're going to see you soon.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they never let those people out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They gave them the passport.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They prepared themselves.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they never let them go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And unfortunately, in 19-- later on, I mean, you find out from different people that all those young women with their children were the first one to go to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But during-- from 1939 till '41, we got a few letters from Germany-- from Poland or Germany, whatever you want to call it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she was miserable, for the whole family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "For me, as a young boy and naturally I still was in school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I wasn't miserable but I was not happy either, I mean, because I know my sisters, my mother is over there, and the uncles and everybody else.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] And then, 1941, in June, the Germans attacked us and we were again on the-- the Germans came in to Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the fighting started off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And one of the Germans threw in a grenade [INAUDIBLE] my father in the house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And somehow they had big ovens, and I was behind.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It's almost like a square box, the ovens, and I was behind over there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And my father was in front of me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the grenade hit him and it saved my life.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
